{"tid":2340151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"呢段判詞算唔算KO晒CC台班冷氣軍師。。。。。。","createTime":"2020-12-25T08:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T12:13:54.000Z","uid":7439,"like":21,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"89c381f2c2eda299bad2bdc8c4301f72f129ee91","tid":2340151,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:13:35.000Z","msg":"咁能勁，唔怪得去咗做國安法指定法官。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>（陳廣池）<br />\n  高等法院原訟法庭暫委法官</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=110870&amp;QS=%28HCMA%2C151%2F2016%29&amp;TP=JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fsearch%2Fsearch_result_detail_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D110870%26QS%3D%2528HCMA%252C151%252F2016%2529%26TP%3DJU&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=8e3d7591\" target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search_result_detail_frame.jsp?DIS=110870&amp;QS=%28HCMA%2C151%2F2016%29&amp;TP=JU</a><br />\n事實上，從留言字句來看，<span class=\"red\">上訴人有如「黃袍加身」，在網絡世界中「閉門造車」，儼然自命為總司令<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，指揮群眾，煽惑那些閱覽留言的群眾真的會去付諸行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，愚昧地依照一個他們可能素未謀面的「指揮官」，到「戰場」進行涉及暴力的罪行。上訴人以為這可使他「置身事外」，繼而從旁觀看他的「戰績」。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本席認為如果有人有勇氣，有膽量去「指揮」群眾鬥爭，指罵對方是「狗隻」、「狗車」，可以那麼「豪情壯語」，為何卻沒有膽量和勇氣去承擔責任？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ace3f9b57cf3eab99bfa60cd2f84665577a038d","tid":2340151,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"一見到潮聯小巴就知係回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5c81a6547de73d7c01aaaa4a17a61f6607ae9e","tid":2340151,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"搵佢都冇用了.......<br />\n<br />\n上訴人：由范黃曹律師行轉聘劉偉聰大律師代表出庭<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/130041044_1293361797685766_579023050066608478_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=sGIbl_KmcU0AX9eEJW9&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=a5f13a5a88e501c6dde4122fe6e4fe24&amp;oe=600B87EF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F130041044_1293361797685766_579023050066608478_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DsGIbl_KmcU0AX9eEJW9%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Da5f13a5a88e501c6dde4122fe6e4fe24%26oe%3D600B87EF&h=335d0721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n24.  上訴人一方在其補充陳詞引用特區訴陳宥羲[14]，重申「正是由於互聯網明顯具有分享資訊、傳閱及報導力能(能力)，難以貿然憑信息內容確定發佈者必然懷有相關『煽惑』意圖，因此有關定罪並不穩妥」[15]。<br />\n25.  首先上訴人運用他的權利，沒有出庭作供。法庭當然不能因此對上訴人有不利的推論，<span class=\"red\">但這亦表示上訴人並不能以第一身的身份提供資料。原審裁判官亦有權就上訴人在錄影會面中的開脫部份不給予任何比重。</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/html/vetted/other/en/2013/FACC000003_2013_files/FACC000003_2013CS.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fhtml%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fen%2F2013%2FFACC000003_2013_files%2FFACC000003_2013CS.htm&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=add70e18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/html/vetted/other/en/2013/FACC000003_2013_files/FACC000003_2013CS.htm</a><br />\n<span class=\"small\">本院承認，就有違公德罪行而言，互聯網是否公衆地方，是一項新鮮的爭議。本院裁定，該罪行的公衆元素需要有關行爲是在一處實質、實際存在的地方作出。互聯網不是一處具有任何實質或實在意義的地方。在該互聯網論壇上看到該段信息的讀者，可能在不同的地方取覽或下載該網頁。在該等實在的地方，而非某一虛擬的地方，他們可能覺得該信息不合乎道德。<span class=\"red\">就該罪行而言，互聯網是一種媒介，而非一處地方。據此，該罪行未能滿足公衆元素的要求。</span><br />\n本院指出，就該罪行而言，本院裁定互聯網並非一處地方的效果，並不意味永遠不能因在某互聯網論壇上的信息而干犯該罪行。在某互聯網論壇上的某項信息，可能在一處實質存在，而公衆能到達或作出有關行爲的地方能被公衆目睹的地方被看到。然而，本案欠缺充分的證據證明本案是否可能就是上述的情況。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a429c637dcd3c2947f0cc71288fb18ccf3a74950","tid":2340151,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"法官係會員沙洛文卡勞"},{"pid":"dfe79de7aac89d264129338f378f5316d87a3a69","tid":2340151,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab6db346d692eb813009a492dda7332268b9e840","tid":2340151,"uid":7439,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"dfe79de7aac89d264129338f378f5316d87a3a69","tid":2340151,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:23:01.000Z","msg":"講真我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76a5c60a9436d1c56c883ce044f3ee8ad17d76d","tid":2340151,"uid":69395,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"dfe79de7aac89d264129338f378f5316d87a3a69","tid":2340151,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:24:37.000Z","msg":"樓主日日睇立會發言紀錄+判詞+正苦新聞網，你咪懵盛盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409da8d81f7343cddc111f18a433eedcc843a0f2","tid":2340151,"uid":7439,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"dfe79de7aac89d264129338f378f5316d87a3a69","tid":2340151,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"波台嚟講真係冇人鍾意講呢隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGvExCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtGvExCN.jpg&h=347da4bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d166822642fb3a15b5f778eb845340d7573a307","tid":2340151,"uid":69395,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ab6db346d692eb813009a492dda7332268b9e840","tid":2340151,"uid":7439,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"dfe79de7aac89d264129338f378f5316d87a3a69","tid":2340151,"uid